                        <h3>Our Story</h3>
                        <p>Blades LLC is a family-owned and operated business, proudly serving the Stroudsburg, Bartonsville, Scotrun, Tannersville, and East Stroudsburg areas since 2021. Our commitment to providing high-quality lawn care services is deeply rooted in our dedication to our community and our customers. Fully insured and with years of expertise, we deliver exceptional results with every job.</p>

                        <p>We understand the importance of a well-maintained lawn, and our mission is to ensure that your property always looks its best. From lawn mowing to landscaping, we bring the care and attention your lawn deserves, and we pride ourselves on building long-term relationships with our clients based on trust and excellent service.</p>

                        <h3>Our Service Areas</h3>
                        <p>We proudly provide our lawn care and landscaping services in:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Stroudsburg</li>
                            <li>Bartonsville</li>
                            <li>Scotrun</li>
                            <li>Tannersville</li>
                            <li>East Stroudsburg</li>
                        </ul>

                        <p>No matter where you are located within these areas, we bring the same level of dedication to your property. Whether it’s a small residential yard or a large commercial lawn, we have the experience and equipment to handle it all.</p>
                    </section>

